data.description:
Welcome to your dream villa tucked away in the highly sought-after community of Indian Trail Villas. Situated on an oversized lot this updated one-story end unit features 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by a meticulously landscaped entrance that features a private paver patio and a zen-like rock garden.As you step inside, a spacious foyer awaits, which flows seamlessly into an open floorplan where the living room, dining room, and kitchen come together and create one large living space. The beautifully updated kitchen features white cabinetry, granite countertops, and a tile backsplash. Additionally, sliding glass doors in the kitchen provide access to the private patio and a generously sized storage closet. From the kitchen, you'll overlook the spacious living room and dining room, which also features sliding glass doors that lead out to a private backyard covered patio. Here you'll be able to enjoy Florida living all year long!

Back inside the master bedroom retreat offers a serene view of the private backyard and features an en-suite bathroom that underwent a complete renovation in 2020. The second bedroom is equally inviting, with an extended closet and sliding glass doors that leads to a private patio. The guest bathroom underwent a complete renovation in 2020 as well.

Additional features include tile and laminate floors throughout, alarm system, hurricane protection, 2014 roof (replaced by HOA), 2020 water heater, 2017 AC unit (still under warranty), 2018 full-size washer and dryer, which are located in the laundry closet off the kitchen. The oversized lot provides enough space for a possible addition of a garage or living square footage (proper permits and HOA approval would be required)

Indian Trail Villas is an all-ages community conveniently located on the west side of Royal Palm Beach Blvd just north of Okeechobee Blvd. The low quarterly dues of $830 include Comcast cable, lawn care, exterior pest control, and access to the community pool. Great schools are only minutes away along with shopping, dining, and entertainment. Indian Trail Villas offers easy access to the Palm Beach International Airport (less than 13 miles away), Florida Turnpike (7 miles away), and Florida's sandy beaches (less than 14 miles away).

With its prime location, updated features, and ample outdoor space, this villa is not just a home, but a sanctuary where you can truly unwind and enjoy the best that Florida living has to offer. Don't miss your chance to make it yours today!
